OL,3,C#9m fund announced for grassroots
OL,4,Cfootball facilities
OL,6,FA #9 million fund has been announced
OL,7,Fto improve facilities for grassroots
OL,8,Ffootball in Northern Ireland.
OL,10,FCommunities Minister Gordon Lyons said
OL,11,Fthe pilot stage of the Grassroots
OL,12,FFacilities Programme will start to
OL,13,Faddress an urgent need in the sector
OL,14,Fof almost 600 clubs.
OL,16,FIt comes as the next milestone in the
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland Football Fund.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
