OL,3,C#9m fund announced for grassroots
OL,4,Cfootball facilities
OL,6,FThe pilot phase of the Grassroots
OL,7,FFacilities Programme is to be
OL,8,Fallocated an indicative budget of #9
OL,9,Fmillion.
OL,11,FFunding awards between #500,000 and
OL,12,F#1.5 million are up for grabs, with
OL,13,Fthe first awards payable to applicants
OL,14,Fas early as financial year 2026/2027.
OL,16,FMr Lyons described an "important
OL,17,Fstart" to addressing the need.
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
