OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772733968
OL,3,C#9m fund announced for grassroots
OL,4,Cfootball facilities
OL,6,F"I am pleased to launch the first call
OL,7,Ffor applications to the Grassroots
OL,8,FFacilities Programme Pilot to begin
OL,9,Faddressing the urgent need for
OL,10,Fimproved facilities at this level," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"The #9 million of funding to kick-
OL,14,Fstart this pilot phase is another
OL,15,Fmajor investment that will support six
OL,16,Fprojects and start delivering the
OL,17,Fmodern facilities our communities
OL,18,Fdeserve.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772733968
OL,3,C#9m fund announced for grassroots
OL,4,Cfootball facilities
OL,6,F"I know this sector needs
OL,7,Fsignificantly more investment, and I
OL,8,Fam under no doubt about the scale of
OL,9,Fthe challenge. This pilot is an
OL,10,Fimportant start."
OL,12,FHe said his officials will deliver
OL,13,Finformation sessions to help clubs
OL,14,Fprepare applications.
OL,16,F"This scheme reflects the value I
OL,17,Fplace on grassroots football and the
OL,18,Frole it plays in our communities," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]xD@AOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
