PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1772733968
OL,3,C#9m fund announced for grassroots
OL,4,Cfootball facilities
OL,6,F"There are almost 600 grassroots
OL,7,Ffootball clubs operating across the
OL,8,Fcountry, and I have seen first-hand on
OL,9,Fvisits to clubs both large and small
OL,10,Fthe contribution they make.
OL,12,F"Whether you play, coach, volunteer,
OL,13,For cheer from the sidelines,
OL,14,Fgrassroots football brings people
OL,15,Ftogether, supports health and
OL,16,Fwellbeing and strengthens our local
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,19,F"This pilot will start to directly
OL,20,Faddress the significant improvements
OL,21,Frequired in grassroots facilities."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@AOU}D@cO]
